      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0008",
      "text": "Discover N_Port/Service Parameters (PDISC)",
      "bbox": [
        133.8,
        190.97,
        347.09,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0009",
      "text": "4.2.31.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        192.63,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0010",
      "text": "The PDISC ELS shall transfer Service Parameters from the initiating Nx_Port to the Nx_Port associ-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.06,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0011",
      "text": "ated with the D_ID without affecting the operating environment between the two ports.  This provides",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.95,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0012",
      "text": "the means for exchange of Service Parameters without terminating open Sequences or open Ex-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.11,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0013",
      "text": "changes.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        136.49,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0014",
      "text": "4.2.31.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        178.22,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0015",
      "text": "a) PDISC Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        322.96,
        200.73,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0016",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        346.96,
        287.89,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0017",
      "text": "4.2.31.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        227.06,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0018",
      "text": "The Payload in PDISC and the LS_ACC are, except for the ELS_Command, identical to the Pay-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.16,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0019",
      "text": "loads in PLOGI (see 4.2.7) and the corresponding LS_ACC (see 4.3.2).  The interchange of PDISC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.88,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0020",
      "text": "information shall not modify the operating environment or Service Parameters between the two ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        540.13,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0021",
      "text": "Service Parameters contained in PDISC shall be ignored and no error condition shall be reported.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        527.06,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0022",
      "text": "4.2.31.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        214.86,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0023",
      "text": "A response shall not be sent to a PDISC if a LR or loop initialization occurs before the LS_ACC is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        539.94,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0024",
      "text": "sent.  An LS_ACC for a PDISC shall be ignored if a LR or loop initialization occurred between the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.85,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p107_s0025",
      "text": "PDISC and the LS_ACC.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        207.07,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
